name: Panorama taken from the Arosa Weisshorn
description:
From where this panorama was taken, you can enjoy breathtaking views of more than 400 mountain peaks in Switzerland and neighbouring countries. This image is the result of five separate photos stitched together in photoshop. All were taken on a Pentax K10D and  other than the stitching, no other edits were made to the image. 

At 2,653m above sea level, the Weisshorn is the highest peak in the Arosa region that can be reached by cable car. This photo image is the result of five different photos stitched together in photoshop. All were taken on a Pentax K10D 

The full image dimensions are: W - 16100 x H - 2246 at 200 PPI.
